title: Week 14 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Sneak N’ Leak - Fantasy Football Podcast for 12/13
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 14! Which performances are the most surprising and the most worrisome as we enter the fantasy football playoffs? Plus, injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for December 13th, 2021.
